data.text:
The easiest way to get to Janjevo/a is by bus from Prishtina. The journey takes 30 minutes and costs 80 cents. Tickets can be bought on the bus. Buses leave from the designated bus stop across from the ‘Ali Sokoli’ medical secondary school at the roundabout at the southern entrance to Prishtina.

Bus Schedules:

Janjeva/o – Prishtina

07:00h, 11:30h, 15:30h, and 17:30h.

Prishtina – Janjeva/o

08:00h, 13:30h, 16:30h, and 19:00h.
